    "Description": "HURSTON DYNAMICS OUTSOURCING\nCONTRACT: Neutralize Hostile Force\nOUTSOURCE MANAGER: T. Dalik\nRISK ASSESSMENT: High\n\nOur security forces have been notified of an ongoing outlaw incursion at ~mission(Location|Address), and we are in need of an independent operator capable of clearing out the hostile actors. \n\nAccording to onsite personnel, the outlaws are currently holed up near the ~mission(Location). Approach with caution and be prepared to use lethal force if the outlaws resist being removed.\n\nPayment will only be authorized once the location has been effectively cleared.\n\n\n\n\n** The information transmitted may contain confidential and/or privileged material. Any review, retransmission, dissemination, or other use of or taking action in reliance upon this information by persons or entities other than the intended recipient is prohibited. **",
